Company Overview of EIG Management Company, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
EIG Management Company, LLC is a privately owned investment manager. It primarily provides its services to private pooled investment vehicles. The firm manages separate client-focused portfolios. It also launches and manages investment funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. It employs combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis to create its portfolio. The firm conducts in-house research to make its investments. It typically invests in energy sector. The firm was formerly known as Energy and Infrastructure Group of Trust Company of the West. EIG Management Company, LLC was founded in November, 2010 and is based in Wash...
EIG Management Company, LLC is a privately owned investment manager. It primarily provides its services to private pooled investment vehicles. The firm manages separate client-focused portfolios. It also launches and manages investment funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. It employs combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis to create its portfolio. The firm conducts in-house research to make its investments. It typically invests in energy sector. The firm was formerly known as Energy and Infrastructure Group of Trust Company of the West. EIG Management Company, LLC was founded in November, 2010 and is based in Washington, District of Columbia.
Detailed Description


