TCW To Move Forward With Sale To Carlyle Despite EIG Suit
A California federal judge issued an injunction Friday allowing TCW Group Inc.'s to sell its assets to the Carlyle Group LP as long as it meets certain conditions, after TCW's joint venture partner EIG Global Energy Partners LLC fought to block the deal.


