V. CONCLUSION

In accordance with the foregoing, the Court hereby GRANTS plaintiff’s request for

a preliminary injunction. Plaintiff within five days of the issuance of this order shall
post a bond in the amount of $50,000. 

IT IS SO ORDERED.

